org.dsngroup.broke.client.metadata

Class ClientSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dsngroup.broke.client.metadata.ClientSession

  • public class ClientSession
extends java.lang.Object
    Client session. Each client should have only one client session. Maintain a reference of publish message queue for back-pressure status monitoring. The operation of publish message queue is performed outside. (e.g. poll(), offer() at the user's coding space.)
